ve to pay yourself later."],[3830,3908,"Oh."],[4202,4312,"Congratulations!"],[4396,4630,"You have won our hidden great price."],[4630,4872,"The food you've ordered today is free of charge,"],[4882,5210,"and also we are giving you the lifetime VIP card."],[5210,5410,"It can be used in our restaurant"],[5410,5570,"at a limited cost."],[5832,5916,"Oh, thank you."],[6450,6510,"Me?"],[6510,6560,"Yep."],[6616,6696,"It's for you."],[6890,6965,"Wow."],[6980,7250,"Aren't I a lucky girl today?"],[7296,7379,"You know, since"],[7379,7567,"I now have exclusive ownership"],[7567,7686,"over this restaurant,"],[7690,7892,"maybe you could remove these two."]],"32":[[10,220,"Fiona, you're going too far."],[220,396,"Remember, I could still divorce you."],[412,536,"Then let's do it."],[552,670,"How about today?"],[692,770,"You little-"],[770,872,"Sweetie, it's okay."],[946,1140,"Don't forget, Henry,"],[1140,1406,"your parents still want me to give you a baby."],[1416,1586,"So, I'd be smart."],[1640,1732,"Just remember,"],[1732,1874,"and let me remind you"],[1874,2066,"that you still owe us a lot of money,"],[2076,2280,"and I can screw you over."],[2876,2976,"Try me."],[4292,4460,"If you see her around the mall again,"],[4480,4606,"you know what to do, right?"],[4656,4711,"Don,"],[4711,4900,"what is your relationship with this lady?"],[4910,5110,"Why are you giving her so much special treatment?"],[5192,5272,"I serve her."],[5346,5426,"You?"],[5496,5559,"Serve her?"],[5578,5672,"Yes."],[5752,5890,"I'm at her service."],[6556,6602,"Hey."],[6650,6760,"I want to see you."],[6796,6876,"Right now?"],[6886,7020,"Yeah, right now."],[7020,7216,"Actually, I changed my mind."],[7216,7466,"I'm in Philly but I'll see you later tonight."],[7586,7674,"Excuse me."],[7674,7810,"Could you point me in the direction"],[7810,7972,"to your nearest hair salon?"],[7972,8082,"I have a date tonight"],[8082,8230,"and I need to knock him dead."],[8360,8556,"Get me the best stylist in Philadelphia."],[8564,8620,"What?"],[8626,8806,"She said she's gonna knock me dead tonight."],[8810,8936,"I need to look fucking good."],[8966,9052,"Come on, move it."]],"33":[[3620,3770,"So, this is what you meant by fun?"],[3822,3996,"The fun I meant is me."],[5806,5970,"And what are you waiting for?"]],"34":[[352,432,"What?"],[546,680,"You're tapping out already."],[702,840,"I'm gonna go shower,"],[840,1076,"and then we'll see who really can't keep going."],[3392,3642,"Fiona, you ruined our date tonight."],[3642,3734,"And now you're screwing around"],[3734,3846,"with some other man?"],[3846,3942,"She's showering."],[3982,4242,"Look, I'll tell her to call you back when we're finished,"],[4252,4320,"alright?"],[4320,4426,"Who is this?"],[4476,4582,"Where are you?"],[5086,5180,"Don't worry, sweetheart."],[5200,5392,"I'll make her pay for what she did tonight."],[5876,6120,"Hi, is this the police department?"],[6196,6340,"I have something I need to report."]],"35":[[832,956,"What is this?"],[1336,1422,"A gift."],[1746,1996,"Look, I just happen to be in Philadelphia."],[2020,2162,"Not for you, I'm just saying..."],[2166,2286,"I saw these shoes,"],[2392,2540,"thought of you, and had to get them."],[2606,2686,"You like it?"],[2816,2926,"Of course I do."],[2960,3176,"I love anything that sparkles."],[4352,4436,"Thank you."],[4462,4602,"Thank me in other ways."],[5542,5639,"Whoa, whoa, whoa."],[5676,5980,"We received a report about illegal activities here."],[5986,6170,"Please cooperate with our investigation."]],"36":[[80,245,"Officer, we're a couple."],[245,289,"Yeah."],[289,530,"There's nothing illegal going on here."],[540,737,"Please, show us your IDs,"],[737,840,"so we can check them."],[1316,1512,"Miss, you said this man is your boyfriend?"],[1552,1632,"Yep."],[1660,1756,"Then what's his name?"],[1876,1956,"His age?"],[1984,2074,"Seriously?"],[2168,2290,"Philly jail..."],[2386,2540,"This is how it ends."],[2606,2686,"Alright."],[2756,2929,"We're not in a relationship."],[2929,2986,"It's actual